WEBVTT

00:00:08.378 --> 00:00:12.486
IT IS MAY TWENTY THIRD NINETEEN NINETY FIVE,

00:00:12.675 --> 00:00:16.459
WE ARE INTERVIEWING RACHEL GOLDBERG. THIS IS TAPE NUMBER TWO

00:00:20.351 --> 00:00:27.027
LET'S CONTINUE WITH YOUR RECOLLECTIONS OF WHAT WARSAW LOOKED LIKE WHEN THE GERMANS INVADED.

00:00:30.666 --> 00:00:35.333
s'iz gevezn zeyer a groyse iberlebenish

00:00:35.380 --> 00:00:40.714
far mayn mishpokhe tsu farlirn dem dakh ibern kop, vi yidn zogn.

00:00:41.095 --> 00:00:47.571
m'hot zikh gevalgert fun eyn korev tsum tsveytn, fun eyn bakantn tsum tsveytn.

00:00:48.619 --> 00:00:51.809
un eyn mol hob ikh gehert az me,

00:00:52.047 --> 00:00:59.713
me geyt gebn a SOUP far di mentshn

00:00:59.951 --> 00:01:04.760
vos es voynen in dem an andern gegnt. bin ikh gegangen in yenem gegnt,

00:01:05.284 --> 00:01:10.903
un s'iz geven a groyse reye mit mentshn tsu krign di SOUP.

00:01:13.427 --> 00:01:16.999
un ikh bin geshtanen un kh'hob getrakht:

00:01:17.665 --> 00:01:24.189
"vifl mol kenstu shteyn tsu nemen a SOUP?"

00:01:25.284 --> 00:01:35.665
mayne eltern hob ikh gevust az zey veln nisht geyn. zey veln nisht esn un zey veln nisht shteyn. hob ikh es gemakht. mayn shvester iz geven tsu yung, bin ikh geven der.

00:01:38.237 --> 00:01:44.665
"vifl mol," kh'hob geredt tsu zikh, "vifl mol, RACHEL, kenstu shteyn azoy?

00:01:45.046 --> 00:01:48.665
dos iz dos ershte un dos letste mol!

00:01:48.808 --> 00:01:54.570
kh'hob a bisl, kh'hob a bisl, gefiln far mentshheyt,

00:01:54.903 --> 00:01:58.427
un ikh trakht az dos iz nisht far dir.

00:01:58.427 --> 00:02:00.808
zukh an andern oysveg."

00:02:00.808 --> 00:02:04.808
kh'hob gezen m'hot genumen di shtekhedike drotn

00:02:04.903 --> 00:02:09.475
un m'hot gemakht a bariere.

00:02:09.475 --> 00:02:17.570
m'hot iber-geteylt Varshe un dos iz geven a tseykhn vu di geto vet shteyn.

00:02:19.856 --> 00:02:22.617
ikh bin aheymgekumen mit di SOUP.

00:02:23.808 --> 00:02:26.998
un s'iz geven take dos ershte un dos letste mol.

00:02:27.379 --> 00:02:33.903
un kh'hob gezogt tsu mayne eltern, az ikh hob detsidirt tsu farlozn Poyln.

00:02:35.332 --> 00:02:38.189
vu vet men geyn?

00:02:38.379 --> 00:02:41.141
kh'hob gehert fun fraynt,

00:02:41.237 --> 00:02:44.903
s'iz zikh tsunoyfgekumen fun tsayt tsu tsayt un m'hot geredt,

00:02:45.474 --> 00:02:48.855
az mentshn dertloyfn keyn Byalistok,

00:02:48.902 --> 00:02:53.760
oyfn veg vern zey dershosn, oder zey kumen tsurik vayl es,

00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:57.379
di lage dort iz zeyer, zeyer a shvere.

00:02:57.664 --> 00:03:07.998
s'hot zikh tsuzamen genumen a shtetl Byalistok, efsher hundert toyznt, efsher tsvey hundert toyznt mentshn, m'shloft oyf di gas, m'shloft in shuln,

00:03:08.617 --> 00:03:13.569
un dos iz oykh nisht keyn oysveg, ober s'vet zayn beser.

00:03:15.236 --> 00:03:21.426
kh'hob getrakht m'vet loyfn dorem.

00:03:23.617 --> 00:03:29.998
kh'hob getrakht kh'vel geyn tsu mayne frayndines, ikh vel zey zogn vos ikh hob detsidirt.

00:03:30.236 --> 00:03:37.617
zey zenen maskem geven ober zey zenen nisht geven greyt tsu farlozn Varshe veyl zey hobn nokh gegat a dakh ibern kop.

00:03:38.712 --> 00:03:42.474
alzo, hob ikh gezogt tsu mayne eltern,

00:03:42.474 --> 00:03:45.236
ikh veys nisht vu Khaim iz yetst,

00:03:45.236 --> 00:03:47.712
oyb er iz in gefangenshaft,

00:03:47.712 --> 00:03:50.950
vayl di daytshn hobn tsuzamen genumen ale

00:03:50.950 --> 00:03:54.759
zelner, geheysn avekleygn dos gever

00:03:54.855 --> 00:04:03.331
un genumen zey in alerley pletser in Poyln un me ken nisht visn vu.

00:04:05.045 --> 00:04:08.712
kh'hob gezogt az kh'vel forn keyn Kuzmir,

00:04:08.712 --> 00:04:13.331
un kh'vil zogn Khayimen az ikh hob detsidirt avektsugeyn

00:04:13.331 --> 00:04:18.045
un hern vegn im vos a meynung er iz.

00:04:20.616 --> 00:04:25.521
iz er geven take in daytshishn plen, vi men zogt.

00:04:25.521 --> 00:04:30.855
er hot zikh fun dortn aroysgekrign mit a bite.

00:04:31.283 --> 00:04:38.140
s'gevez- s'iz gevezn a a zakh tsu bashraybn. s'iz geven efsher a nes, ikh ken nisht zogn.

00:04:38.140 --> 00:04:41.188
ikh gloyb nisht zeyer shtark keyn NISSIM.

00:04:41.188 --> 00:04:47.238
alzo, kh'hob detsidirt az shabes oder zuntik

00:04:47.238 --> 00:04:52.000
vel ikh forn mit di ban keyn Kuzmir, KAZIMIERZ.

00:04:53.714 --> 00:04:58.142
lebn KAZIMIERZ iz geven a shtetl hot geheysn Polave.

00:04:58.378 --> 00:05:03.950
dort- fun dort shtamt mayn mame. s'iz geven fertsn kilometer, s'iz azoy a bald

00:05:04.045 --> 00:05:08.664
a na- hunder- nayn MILES fun eyn shtetl in di andere arayn.

00:05:08.807 --> 00:05:11.235
a sakh mentshn zenen gegangen tsu fus,

00:05:11.235 --> 00:05:15.045
vayl di ban iz geblibn shteyn in Polave.

00:05:15.045 --> 00:05:20.759
dernokh hot men gedorfn nemen a BUS, oder a ferd mit a vogn, o- oder geyn oyf di-

00:05:20.807 --> 00:05:24.521
oyf di leven, heyst, oyf- tsu fus.

00:05:27.711 --> 00:05:32.901
mayn mame hot gezogt, m'vet dikh aroysvarfn fun di ban. az zey trefn a yid

00:05:32.901 --> 00:05:37.901
makhn zey oyf se fentster un varfn aroys in mitn gang fun di ban.

00:05:38.378 --> 00:05:42.378
ober s'hot- kh'hob mikh nisht opgeshrokn fun dem.

00:05:44.044 --> 00:05:46.425
ober s'iz geshen an andere zakh.

00:05:46.425 --> 00:05:51.616
far shabes, fraytik, iz Khaim gekumen tsun undz.

00:05:51.711 --> 00:05:56.092
di zelbe tsayt vos ikh hob detsidirt tsu farlozn Varshe,

00:05:56.187 --> 00:06:00.330
hot er detsidirt tsu farlozn Poyln.

00:06:00.711 --> 00:06:04.330
un er iz gekumen mir dos zogn.

00:06:04.330 --> 00:06:09.854
kh'hob im dertseylt az di detsizye b- bay undz iz gekumen di zelbe tsayt,

00:06:09.854 --> 00:06:12.140
efsher dem zelbn tog!

00:06:12.140 --> 00:06:15.092
un er hot mir dertseylt vos er hot ibergelebt

00:06:15.092 --> 00:06:17.997
un far vos er muz farlozn.

00:06:17.997 --> 00:06:21.092
keyn andere veg iz nisht gevezn.

00:06:21.663 --> 00:06:26.949
keyn andere veg iz nisht gevezn, nor tsu geyn oyf di rusishe teritorye.

00:06:27.687 --> 00:06:32.119
BUT YOU- YOU LEFT WITH CHAIM AND YOUR MOTHER AND SARAH STAYED...

00:06:32.853 --> 00:06:36.472
I LEFT, ikh hob farlozt Varshe

00:06:36.711 --> 00:06:41.520
mit Khaim, mayn tate iz alt geven eyn un fuftsik yor.

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:44.663
er hot gezogt azoy. "her oys mayn tokhter.

00:06:44.758 --> 00:06:49.472
ikh vel dikh nisht lozn mit a mans-pershoyn geyn aleyn. ikh gey mit."

00:06:50.806 --> 00:06:54.171
un, er hot nisht gegat vos tsu farlirn in Varshe-

00:06:53.856 --> 00:06:58.570
SO YOU AND CHAIM AND YOUR FATHER LEFT. YOUR MOTHER AND SARAH STAYED...

00:06:56.284 --> 00:06:57.542
yo.

00:06:57.542 --> 00:06:59.799
m'hot gekoyft biletn.

00:06:59.853 --> 00:07:05.568
shteyendik in di reye tsu koyfn biletn oyf di ban iz tsugekumen tsun undz

00:07:05.568 --> 00:07:08.806
a krist un er hot gezogt azoy,

00:07:08.806 --> 00:07:11.949
"ikh veys vu ets geyt, vu ets vilt geyn.

00:07:12.091 --> 00:07:15.948
azoy vi di ban vet zikh opshteln oyf di letste stantsye,

00:07:15.948 --> 00:07:23.187
zolt ets vartn oyf mir, ikh vel tsun enk tsukumen, un ikh vel enk helfn ariber geyn bay nakht di grenets."

00:07:23.377 --> 00:07:26.044
oyser gevenlekh! a...

00:07:26.187 --> 00:07:34.663
s'hot zikh bavizn aza mentsh, un s'iz geshtanen azoy fil mentshn in di reye nokh di biletn, un tsu keynem iz er nisht tsugegangen nor tsun undz!

00:07:36.282 --> 00:07:40.520
un s'iz azoy geven. er hot undz arayngefirt in a voynung,

00:07:40.520 --> 00:07:44.996
dort ven, ven m'iz gekumen mit di ban di letste STOP.

00:07:45.234 --> 00:07:48.377
er hot undz arayn gefirt in a voynung, er hot gezogt azoy.

00:07:48.377 --> 00:07:54.234
"biz farnakht et ets do shteyn. do vet ets esn

00:07:54.234 --> 00:08:00.234
un az- far nakht, eyder s'vert in gantsn fintster, vel ikh kumen

00:08:00.234 --> 00:08:03.948
un ikh vel enk aroysfirn oyfn veg."

00:08:03.948 --> 00:08:08.329
hot men zikh opgeshmuest az mir veln im gebn,

00:08:08.329 --> 00:08:10.187
er hot gefregt vos mir hobn.

00:08:10.234 --> 00:08:13.091
hob ikh gegat oyringlekh, goldene oyringlekh.

00:08:13.091 --> 00:08:16.520
un mayn shvester hot aropgenumen ire goldene oyringlekh.

00:08:16.615 --> 00:08:21.853
dernokh hob ikh gegat a feder mit a goldene POINT,

00:08:21.853 --> 00:08:26.615
vos Khaim's bruder hot mir gegebn a matone vayl kh'hob im epes tsugelernt.

00:08:27.663 --> 00:08:32.282
kh'hob gegat zeyf, zalts un tsuker,

00:08:32.377 --> 00:08:36.044
un dos zenen geven di vikhtikste zakhn vos er hot gevolt.

00:08:36.234 --> 00:08:39.623
dos gold iz im nisht geven azoy vikhtik vi di zalts,

00:08:39.752 --> 00:08:40.557
SUGAR.

00:08:40.740 --> 00:08:42.710
tsuker un zeyf.

00:08:44.663 --> 00:08:50.710
ven vet men es dir gebn? ven m'vet zayn in di ershte rusishe-

00:08:50.710 --> 00:08:54.186
oyf di rusishe toyer. gut?

00:08:54.901 --> 00:08:58.663
far nakht iz er gekumen,

00:08:58.663 --> 00:09:02.663
er hot, hot gezogt mir zoln im nokhgeyn.

00:09:03.472 --> 00:09:06.948
un m'iz geganen, s'iz shoyn geven zeyer shpet bay nakht.

00:09:07.043 --> 00:09:10.948
m'iz gekumen tsu a plats, m'iz gegan nokh a vald.

00:09:11.472 --> 00:09:14.567
Khaim hot es bamoln.

00:09:14.567 --> 00:09:19.091
er hot a tseykhenung vi mir geyen adurkh di grenets,

00:09:19.091 --> 00:09:21.091
un er hot a bild

00:09:21.662 --> 00:09:26.996
vos es vayzt vi mir geyen adurkh dem grenets un vi nokh mayn mame iz adurkh di grenets.

00:09:26.996 --> 00:09:31.377
a shutfesdike, a por epizodn oyf eyn bild.

00:09:31.520 --> 00:09:39.091
ikh volt gevolt m'zol es vayzn, nor ikh gloyb m'vet farendikn undzer geshprekh et vern gevizn dos bild.

00:09:39.710 --> 00:09:46.710
ikh - ven m'iz gekumen in tifn vald

00:09:46.710 --> 00:09:49.472
hot der mentsh ongevizn oyf a hoyz,

00:09:49.472 --> 00:09:51.377
er hot gezogt, do voyn ikh.

00:09:51.377 --> 00:09:53.948
yetst darft ets mir gebn alding.

00:09:54.805 --> 00:09:57.234
un ikh vel enk ariberfirn.

00:09:57.662 --> 00:10:00.424
un oyb ets et mir nisht gebn

00:10:00.853 --> 00:10:02.710
loz ikh enk shteyn do.

00:10:03.614 --> 00:10:10.186
un mir hobn gezen nisht vayt fun undz zenen geshtanen daytshn mit biksn,

00:10:10.186 --> 00:10:12.043
zey zenen geganen hin un tsurik.

00:10:12.710 --> 00:10:19.853
un er hot gezogt azoy, "ikh vil di zakhn arayntrogn tsu mir in shtub arayn, ikh vel tsurik kumen ikh vel enk nemen vayter."

00:10:20.900 --> 00:10:22.900
hot men zikh avek gerukt

00:10:25.376 --> 00:10:28.472
un m'hot m'hot zikh avek gerukt

00:10:28.614 --> 00:10:32.662
un m'hot es gemakht a a geshprekh tsvishn undz.

00:10:32.662 --> 00:10:40.091
nisht vayt farn, farn vald hobn zikh tsun undz tsugetshepet tsvey meydlekh,

00:10:40.091 --> 00:10:44.472
tsu dray meydlekh, ikh gedenk nisht. tsvey oder dray meydlekh.

00:10:44.567 --> 00:10:49.756
un zey hobn mir gebetn, azoy vi ikh bin eyn froy mit tsvey mener

00:10:49.756 --> 00:10:55.090
zol ikh zey tsutshepen tsun undz, zikh filn beser in di svive.

00:10:55.090 --> 00:10:58.709
hot men dos geton. oyfn veg hot men zikh farloyrn.

00:10:58.709 --> 00:11:04.423
zey hobn farlorn a pekl, hobn zey zikh aropgeboygn tsuzamen tsu nemen di zakhn

00:11:04.423 --> 00:11:12.709
un der mentsh hot geshrign men muz geyn geshvind vayl do iz zeyer a tragishe forfal gevezn, un m'muz do durkhgeyn geshvind

00:11:12.709 --> 00:11:15.852
u- un zey hobn nisht gekent makhn geshvind un m'hot zey farloyrn,

00:11:15.852 --> 00:11:19.233
di meydlekh. ikh gloyb zey hobn zikh oykh opgeratevet.

00:11:20.566 --> 00:11:25.376
un m'hot detsidirt shtilerheyt tsvishn undz az m'vet im nisht gebn

00:11:26.042 --> 00:11:32.566
ken er, get er undz iber bald tsu di daytshn iz momental, eyn koyl yeder eyner, un dos iz.

00:11:32.899 --> 00:11:36.756
az m'vet im gebn iz nokh do a bisl hofenung.

00:11:37.042 --> 00:11:38.947
a kleyne hofenung.

00:11:39.137 --> 00:11:43.090
m'hot detsidirt m'vet im avekgebn alts vos m'hot im tsugezogt.

00:11:43.613 --> 00:11:47.709
un er hot- hot alts genumen un er iz ariber geshprungen dem,

00:11:47.709 --> 00:11:49.947
dem ployt zaynem,

00:11:49.947 --> 00:11:55.566
un mir zenen geshtanen untern gorn himl, zeendik di daytshn. di daytshn hobn undz nisht gezen.

00:11:55.566 --> 00:11:59.423
zeendik di daytshn, un vartndik

00:11:59.423 --> 00:12:03.042
efsher tsvey minut, efsher dray minut,

00:12:03.042 --> 00:12:05.851
ober s'hot oysgezen vi dray yor.

00:12:06.709 --> 00:12:10.661
m'hot nisht gevust vos undzer goyrl geyt yetst zayn.

00:12:10.661 --> 00:12:12.566
ober der mentsh iz tsurik gekumen.

00:12:12.994 --> 00:12:16.756
er iz tsurik gekumen un er hot undz gefirt vayter.

00:12:16.804 --> 00:12:20.185
un arayngefirt in a vald,

00:12:20.185 --> 00:12:26.566
un dort hot gevoynt, iz geshtanen a h- hoyz un dort hot gevoynt a mentsh vos hot gehitn dem vald.

00:12:26.566 --> 00:12:29.566
dos iz geven a neytrale zone.

00:12:30.470 --> 00:12:33.423
nisht tsu di daytshn hot dos gehert un nisht tsu di rusn.

00:12:33.518 --> 00:12:39.565
ober yede nakht zenen dort gekumen rusn un daytshn zen tsu s'iz nisht do keyn mentshn vos,

00:12:39.565 --> 00:12:41.391
vos sh- s'nekhtikn dort.

00:12:41.473 --> 00:12:42.720
SO WHERE DID THEY HIDE YOU?

00:12:43.089 --> 00:12:46.327
zey hobn undz geleygt oyf der erd.

00:12:46.518 --> 00:12:49.994
ikh bin shoyn gevezn damolst in groysn fiber.

00:12:49.996 --> 00:12:50.507
aha

00:12:50.375 --> 00:12:53.756
kh'bin krank gevorn oyf a tifus oyfn veg.

00:12:53.588 --> 00:12:53.981
oh

00:12:54.098 --> 00:12:54.994
mit fiber.

00:12:55.137 --> 00:12:57.470
kh'hob gegat zeyer a sheyne

00:12:58.137 --> 00:13:03.708
ornament, a broshke, vos Khaim hot mir gemakht un gegebn m- mit a yor frier.

00:13:04.089 --> 00:13:07.899
un kh'hob zey dos gevizn, un m'hot es mir nisht tsurik gegebn.

00:13:07.946 --> 00:13:13.232
un kh'hob nisht geleygt keyn akht vayl kh'bin geven azoy shleferik un azoy mid.

00:13:13.708 --> 00:13:18.089
un m'hot gemuzt detsidirn oyf dem vos er hot zogn.

00:13:18.470 --> 00:13:20.565
er iz dan geganen aheym,

00:13:20.899 --> 00:13:23.756
vayl az m'vet im trefn vet men im shisn.

00:13:23.899 --> 00:13:25.803
iz er gegangen tsurik aheym,

00:13:26.041 --> 00:13:27.945
un mir hobn iber-genekhtikt.

00:13:28.183 --> 00:13:31.517
in der fri iz aroys der hiter,

00:13:31.755 --> 00:13:36.707
un er hot, iz geforn oyf a- oyf a- rover.

00:13:36.802 --> 00:13:38.041
iz er geforn

00:13:38.041 --> 00:13:44.564
zen vi der veg zet oys. er iz tsurik gekumen, er hot gezogt, m'zet nisht keyn daytshn, m'zet nisht keyn rusn,

00:13:44.612 --> 00:13:45.755
lomir geyn.

00:13:46.041 --> 00:13:51.564
un mir zenen geganen, mit nokh im, er iz geganen foroys. teyl mol hot er undz ayngehaltn.

00:13:51.660 --> 00:13:57.469
m'iz geganen foroys, er hot undz gevizn, "zest do zenen shoyn do di rusn."

00:13:57.755 --> 00:14:04.088
un mir hobn gezen, s'iz geven a derfl, mir hobn gezen rusn, un zey hobn undz ayngehaltn.

00:14:04.898 --> 00:14:09.755
militer mener hobn undz ayngehaltn, dos iz geven a grenets shtetele.

00:14:09.993 --> 00:14:13.183
un zey hobn undz gefregt vu me geyt, hobn mir gezogt, me geyt aheym.

00:14:14.469 --> 00:14:18.755
alzo, zey hobn undz azoy oysgelernt zogn.

00:14:19.136 --> 00:14:32.849
fun dort iz men geforn, fun dort iz men geforn mit di ban keyn Byalistok.

00:14:34.040 --> 00:14:38.190
oyfn veg oyf di ban hot Khaim gekrign an atak

00:14:38.373 --> 00:14:41.230
fun SHLEPEKISHE, APPENDIX.

00:14:42.230 --> 00:14:47.230
an atak mit shreklekhe shmertsn. in di ban.

00:14:48.992 --> 00:14:54.516
ober s'iz adurkh, s'iz avek, di shmertsn zenen avek.

00:14:54.516 --> 00:14:57.040
mir zenen farforn keyn Byalistok.

00:14:57.754 --> 00:15:07.897
m'iz arayn in a, in a shul, un ikh bin shoyn gelegn oyfn be- oyf a tish, di kranke.

00:15:08.897 --> 00:15:12.706
un m'hot mikh fun dort gefirt

00:15:12.753 --> 00:15:19.563
in a shpitol arayn, vos ikh bin geven di ershte kranke in a shpitol arayn vos di rusn hobn geefnt.

00:15:19.799 --> 00:15:23.254
THAT'S THE- THAT'S THE HOSPITAL WHERE YOU LEARNED HOW TO SPEAK RUSSIAN?

00:15:23.218 --> 00:15:23.818
yo

00:15:23.381 --> 00:15:24.763
OK, YOU'LL TELL ME ABOUT THAT...

00:15:25.705 --> 00:15:31.801
ikh hob, m'hot mikh a- unterzukht a dokter,

00:15:31.801 --> 00:15:39.692
ale doktoyrim dort, un ale, di di ACHIYOT zenen gevezn yidn.

00:15:39.518 --> 00:15:40.595
yidn.

00:15:39.922 --> 00:15:43.441
yidishe, yo, m'hot azoy m'hot spetsyel mobilizirt yidishe.

